---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | collectif">
	<main>
		<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
		
		<div class="content">
			<section>
				<h2>Our Commitment</h2>
				<p>At collectif, we prioritize privacy and anonymity above all else. Our platform is designed to protect whistleblowers, sources, and users while maintaining the highest standards of operational security.</p>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Data Collection</h2>
				<p>We minimize data collection to protect our users:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>We do not collect personally identifiable information</li>
					<li>We do not use tracking cookies</li>
					<li>We do not maintain user session data</li>
					<li>We do not log IP addresses</li>
					<li>We do not store browser fingerprints</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Anonymous Submissions</h2>
				<p>For whistleblowers and sources:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>All submissions are encrypted end-to-end</li>
					<li>Metadata is stripped from submitted files</li>
					<li>Source identities are never recorded</li>
					<li>Submission logs are automatically purged</li>
				</ul>
			</section>

			<section>
				<h2>Secure Communication</h2>
				<p>For secure communication with our team:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Use our PGP key for encrypted messages</li>
					<li>Connect through Tor for enhanced anonymity</li>
					<li>Use secure drop for sensitive documents</li>
					<li>Avoid including personal identifiers in communications</li>
				</ul>

